! conclusion: If identity invariants are preserved and distortions corrected, [🌆/门 🌝/友]
              the repository becomes an emporium that drives opportunity,
              visibility, and revenue.

  + THEN: Operate an explicit move on the named axis (see substructure below); steward the pattern against the declared discipline.

The repository becomes a training ground for modern research
                   practice rather than an administrative burden.

The repository evolves from a compliance system into an emporium —
                 a public-facing, value-generating showcase of Oxford Brookes’
                 intellectual and creative output.

  + because: Strategy becomes proactive and outward-facing.

  + because: Responsibility becomes a trust surface rather than a bottleneck.

  + because: Connectivity becomes a showcase for interdisciplinary capability.

  + because: Inclusivity becomes visible and embodied in research outputs.

  + because: Development is supported through frictionless contribution.
